        <mxCell id="9GJZZyZrNoLVnp14qoA9-77" parent="9GJZZyZrNoLVnp14qoA9-18" style="text;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;" value="&lt;ul style=&quot;padding-inline-start: 2em; margin-top: 0px; color: rgb(204, 204, 204); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &amp;quot;Segoe UI&amp;quot;, Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(37, 37, 38); text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;&quot;&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;white-space: pre-wrap; margin-top: 0.1em; margin-bottom: 0.2em;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;code style=&quot;font-family: monospace; color: rgb(215, 186, 125); background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1); padding: 2px 4px; border-radius: 3px; word-break: break-word; font-size: 0.9em;&quot;&gt;RegistryView&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/strong&gt; — portão sobre o &lt;code style=&quot;font-family: monospace; color: rgb(215, 186, 125); background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1); padding: 2px 4px; border-radius: 3px; word-break: break-word; font-size: 0.9em;&quot;&gt;StateRegistry&lt;/code&gt; inteiro, sem &lt;code style=&quot;font-family: monospace; color: rgb(215, 186, 125); background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1); padding: 2px 4px; border-radius: 3px; word-break: break-word; font-size: 0.9em;&quot;&gt;subscribe&lt;/code&gt;/&lt;code style=&quot;font-family: monospace; color: rgb(215, 186, 125); background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1); padding: 2px 4px; border-radius: 3px; word-break: break-word; font-size: 0.9em;&quot;&gt;resolve&lt;/code&gt;/&lt;code style=&quot;font-family: monospace; color: rgb(215, 186, 125); background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1); padding: 2px 4px; border-radius: 3px; word-break: break-word; font-size: 0.9em;&quot;&gt;commit&lt;/code&gt;; é quem &lt;em&gt;fabrica&lt;/em&gt; &lt;code style=&quot;font-family: monospace; color: rgb(215, 186, 125); background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1); padding: 2px 4px; border-radius: 3px; word-break: break-word; font-size: 0.9em;&quot;&gt;ReadProxy&lt;/code&gt; (&lt;code style=&quot;font-family: monospace; color: rgb(215, 186, 125); background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1); padding: 2px 4px; border-radius: 3px; word-break: break-word; font-size: 0.9em;&quot;&gt;read_proxy(key)&lt;/code&gt;) sem precisar expor o &lt;code style=&quot;font-family: monospace; color: rgb(215, 186, 125); background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1); padding: 2px 4px; border-radius: 3px; word-break: break-word; font-size: 0.9em;&quot;&gt;Rc&amp;lt;RefCell&amp;lt;StateRegistry&amp;gt;&amp;gt;&lt;/code&gt; cru.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;white-space: pre-wrap; margin-top: 0.1em; margin-bottom: 0.2em;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;code style=&quot;font-family: monospace; color: rgb(215, 186, 125); background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1); padding: 2px 4px; border-radius: 3px; word-break: break-word; font-size: 0.9em;&quot;&gt;snapshot()&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/strong&gt; — pra quando você quer &lt;strong&gt;tudo, sem saber os nomes&lt;/strong&gt;: devolve &lt;code style=&quot;font-family: monospace; color: rgb(215, 186, 125); background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1); padding: 2px 4px; border-radius: 3px; word-break: break-word; font-size: 0.9em;&quot;&gt;Vec&amp;lt;StateSlot&amp;gt;&lt;/code&gt; com &lt;code style=&quot;font-family: monospace; color: rgb(215, 186, 125); background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1); padding: 2px 4px; border-radius: 3px; word-break: break-word; font-size: 0.9em;&quot;&gt;{key, value}&lt;/code&gt; de todo o &lt;code style=&quot;font-family: monospace; color: rgb(215, 186, 125); background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1); padding: 2px 4px; border-radius: 3px; word-break: break-word; font-size: 0.9em;&quot;&gt;CurrentState&lt;/code&gt;, reconstruído sob demanda (zipa &lt;code style=&quot;font-family: monospace; color: rgb(215, 186, 125); background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1); padding: 2px 4px; border-radius: 3px; word-break: break-word; font-size: 0.9em;&quot;&gt;index&lt;/code&gt; + buffer). É caro de propósito (realoca/clona a cada chamada) — serve pra debug/dump ocasional, nunca caminho quente.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="151" width="550" x="635.0038461538458" y="205.99923076923073" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="9GJZZyZrNoLVnp14qoA9-78" parent="9GJZZyZrNoLVnp14qoA9-18" style="text;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;" value="&lt;ul style=&quot;padding-inline-start: 2em; margin-top: 0px; color: rgb(204, 204, 204); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &amp;quot;Segoe UI&amp;quot;, Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(37, 37, 38); text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;&quot;&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;white-space: pre-wrap; margin-top: 0.1em; margin-bottom: 0.2em;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;code style=&quot;font-family: monospace; color: rgb(215, 186, 125); background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1); padding: 2px 4px; border-radius: 3px; word-break: break-word; font-size: 0.9em;&quot;&gt;index: HashMap&amp;lt;String, usize&amp;gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/strong&gt; — o mecanismo operacional real de &quot;nome → posição&quot;. É o que resolve uma &lt;code style=&quot;font-family: monospace; color: rgb(215, 186, 125); background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1); padding: 2px 4px; border-radius: 3px; word-break: break-word; font-size: 0.9em;&quot;&gt;key&lt;/code&gt; pra um &lt;code style=&quot;font-family: monospace; color: rgb(215, 186, 125); background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1); padding: 2px 4px; border-radius: 3px; word-break: break-word; font-size: 0.9em;&quot;&gt;usize&lt;/code&gt; em tempo real, tanto pra &lt;code style=&quot;font-family: monospace; color: rgb(215, 186, 125); background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1); padding: 2px 4px; border-radius: 3px; word-break: break-word; font-size: 0.9em;&quot;&gt;ReadProxy&lt;/code&gt;/&lt;code style=&quot;font-family: monospace; color: rgb(215, 186, 125); background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1); padding: 2px 4px; border-radius: 3px; word-break: break-word; font-size: 0.9em;&quot;&gt;Proxy&lt;/code&gt; (resolvido uma vez, guardado) quanto pra &lt;code style=&quot;font-family: monospace; color: rgb(215, 186, 125); background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1); padding: 2px 4px; border-radius: 3px; word-break: break-word; font-size: 0.9em;&quot;&gt;read(key)&lt;/code&gt;/&lt;code style=&quot;font-family: monospace; color: rgb(215, 186, 125); background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1); padding: 2px 4px; border-radius: 3px; word-break: break-word; font-size: 0.9em;&quot;&gt;read_proxy(key)&lt;/code&gt; (lookup pontual). Vive dentro do &lt;code style=&quot;font-family: monospace; color: rgb(215, 186, 125); background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1); padding: 2px 4px; border-radius: 3px; word-break: break-word; font-size: 0.9em;&quot;&gt;StateRegistry&lt;/code&gt;, é privado, ninguém de fora enxerga isso diretamente.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;white-space: pre-wrap; margin-top: 0.1em; margin-bottom: 0.2em;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;code style=&quot;font-family: monospace; color: rgb(215, 186, 125); background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1); padding: 2px 4px; border-radius: 3px; word-break: break-word; font-size: 0.9em;&quot;&gt;StateSlot { key, value }&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/strong&gt; — não é armazenamento, é metadado reconstruído sob demanda. Só existe como retorno de &lt;code style=&quot;font-family: monospace; color: rgb(215, 186, 125); background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1); padding: 2px 4px; border-radius: 3px; word-break: break-word; font-size: 0.9em;&quot;&gt;snapshot()&lt;/code&gt;: pareia de volta o nome (que &lt;code style=&quot;font-family: monospace; color: rgb(215, 186, 125); background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1); padding: 2px 4px; border-radius: 3px; word-break: break-word; font-size: 0.9em;&quot;&gt;index&lt;/code&gt; sabe) com o valor (que o buffer &lt;code style=&quot;font-family: monospace; color: rgb(215, 186, 125); background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1); padding: 2px 4px; border-radius: 3px; word-break: break-word; font-size: 0.9em;&quot;&gt;Vec&amp;lt;Cell&amp;lt;f64&amp;gt;&amp;gt;&lt;/code&gt; guarda), pra quem quer inspecionar/listar por nome sem já ter um &lt;code style=&quot;font-family: monospace; color: rgb(215, 186, 125); background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1); padding: 2px 4px; border-radius: 3px; word-break: break-word; font-size: 0.9em;&quot;&gt;usize&lt;/code&gt;/&lt;code style=&quot;font-family: monospace; color: rgb(215, 186, 125); background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1); padding: 2px 4px; border-radius: 3px; word-break: break-word; font-size: 0.9em;&quot;&gt;ReadProxy&lt;/code&gt; em mãos.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;white-space: pre-wrap; margin-top: 0.1em; margin-bottom: 0.2em;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Diferença central:&lt;/strong&gt; &lt;code style=&quot;font-family: monospace; color: rgb(215, 186, 125); background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1); padding: 2px 4px; border-radius: 3px; word-break: break-word; font-size: 0.9em;&quot;&gt;index&lt;/code&gt; é a fonte da verdade, consultada toda vez que alguém resolve uma chave; &lt;code style=&quot;font-family: monospace; color: rgb(215, 186, 125); background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1); padding: 2px 4px; border-radius: 3px; word-break: break-word; font-size: 0.9em;&quot;&gt;StateSlot&lt;/code&gt; é só a forma de &lt;em&gt;exibir&lt;/em&gt; um par nome-valor depois que &lt;code style=&quot;font-family: monospace; color: rgb(215, 186, 125); background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1); padding: 2px 4px; border-radius: 3px; word-break: break-word; font-size: 0.9em;&quot;&gt;index&lt;/code&gt; já fez esse trabalho — um é mecanismo, o outro é retrato.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="233" width="833" x="-1080" y="206" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
      </root>
    </mxGraphModel>
  </diagram>
  <diagram name="Threads v1" id="TlFSUXNwAsX9WndVF_uC">
    <mxGraphModel dx="2755" dy="694" grid="0" gridSize="10" guides="1" tooltips="1" connect="1" arrows="1" fold="1" page="0" pageScale="1" pageWidth="1654" pageHeight="1169" math="0" shadow="0">
